DOCUMENT();

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "MathObjects.pl",
  "AnswerFormatHelp.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());

Context("Numeric");

$p = random(2,4,1);
$N = 10**$p;

Context()->texStrings;
BEGIN_TEXT

Rewrite the following statement using a logarithm.  Fill in each blank with the appropriate letter or number.
$PAR
\( 10^{$p} = $N \) is equivalent to \( \log_{10} \big( \) \{ ans_rule(10)  \} \( \big) = \) \{ ans_rule(8) \}
\{ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") \}

END_TEXT
Context()->normalStrings;

$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

ANS(Real("$N")->cmp() );
ANS(Real("$p")->cmp() );

#ANS(num_cmp( $N ) );
#ANS(num_cmp( $p ) );

Context()->texStrings;
SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$PAR
$BBOLD  SOLUTION $EBOLD
$PAR
The statement is equivalent to \( \log_{10}{$N} = $p \).

END_SOLUTION
Context()->normalStrings;

;
ENDDOCUMENT();
